04:44.360 --> 04:46.328
( radio chatter )

04:46.600 --> 04:48.329
MORNING.

04:50.660 --> 04:52.093
OKAY...

04:52.100 --> 04:55.149
WHAT ARE YOU MAD
AT ME ABOUT NOW ?

04:55.160 --> 04:56.422
LOOK, I'M BUSY,
ALRIGHT ?

04:56.430 --> 04:58.455
