ENGAGE YOU IN SMALL TALK

05:00.160 --> 05:02.924
JUST TO MAKE YOU
FEEL BE'I'I'ER.

05:06.000 --> 05:08.059
YOU FLUNKED
THE LICENSING TEST.

05:08.060 --> 05:09.652
DID YOU THINK
I DIDN'T KNOW

05:09.660 --> 05:11.093
THE GRADES WERE
BEING POSTED TODAY ?

05:11.100 --> 05:12.158
I DIDN'T.

05:12.160 --> 05:14.720
YOU DIDN'T
APPLY YOURSELF.

05:14.730 --> 05:16.391
YOU THINK THIS IS
SOMETHING THAT PEOPLE DO

05:16.400 --> 05:17.822
WHEN THEY CAN'T
DO ANYTHING ELSE.

05:17.830 --> 05:19.297
AND THEREFORE, IT CAN'T
BE THAT DIFFICULT.

05:19.300 --> 05:20.756
OKAY, I FEEL PRE'ITY
BAD RIGHT NOW.

05:20.760 --> 05:22.022
IS IT REALLY IMPORTANT
TO MAKE ME FEEL WORSE ?

05:22.030 --> 05:23.122
I DON'T CARE
WHAT YOU FEEL.

05:23.130 --> 05:24.791
OH, BULLSHIT, YOU LIKE
IT WHEN I FEEL BAD

05:24.800 --> 05:26.859
BECAUSE MISERY
LOVES COMPANY.

05:34.130 --> 05:35.529
HOW'D HE DIE ?

05:35.530 --> 05:37.657
H EART ATTACK.

05:37.660 --> 05:39.855
